solidity >=0.4.22 <0.7.0;\npragma experimental ABIEncoderV2;\n\n/**\n * @title Ballot\n * @dev Implements voting process along with vote delegation\n */\ncontract VelasDevelopment {\n    IStakingAuRa public stakingContract;\n\n    struct Voter {\n        uint weight;\n    }\n\n    struct Proposal {\n        string description;\n        string url;\n        uint votesUpWeight;\n        uint votesDownWeight;\n        uint progress;\n        address owner;\n    }\n\n      modifier onlyInitialized {\n        require(isStakingInitialized());\n        _;\n    }\n\n      function isStakingInitialized() public view returns(bool) {\n        return stakingContract != IStakingAuRa(0);\n    }\n\n    mapping(address => Voter) public voters;\n\n    Proposal[] public proposals;\n\n    mapping(bytes32 => uint) public votes;\n\n    constructor(address _stakingContract) public {\n        setStakingAuraAddress(_stakingContract);\n    }\n\n    function setStakingAuraAddress(address _stakingContract) internal {\n        stakingContract = IStakingAuRa(_stakingContract);\n    }\n\n\n    function updateWeight(address voter_address) internal onlyInitialized {\n        Voter storage voter = voters[voter_address];\n        if(voter.weight > 0) return;\n\n        voter.weight = stakingContract.stakeAmountTotal(voter_address);\n    }\n\n    function voteUp(uint proposal) public {\n\n        Voter storage sender = voters[msg.sender];\n        updateWeight(msg.sender);\n        require(sender.weight != 0, \"Has no right to vote\");\n        bytes32 hash = keccak256(abi.encodePacked(msg.sender, proposal));\n        require(votes[hash] == 0);\n        votes[hash] = 1;\n        proposals[proposal].votesUpWeight += sender.weight;\n    }\n\n    function voteDown(uint proposal) public {\n        Voter storage sender = voters[msg.sender];\n        updateWeight(msg.sender);\n        require(sender.weight != 0, \"Has no right to vote\");\n        bytes32 hash = keccak256(abi.encodePacked(msg.sender, proposal));\n        require(votes[hash] == 0);\n        votes[hash] = 1;\n        proposals[proposal].votesDownWeight += sender.weight;\n    }\n\n    function addProposal(string memory description, string memory url, uint progress) payable public {\n        //spam protection\n        require(msg.value >= 1 ether);\n        Proposal memory proposal;\n        proposal.description = description;\n        proposal.url = url;\n        proposal.progress = progress;\n        proposal.owner = msg.sender;\n        proposals.push(proposal);\n    }\n\n    function proposalLength() view public returns(uint) {\n        return proposals.length;\n    }\n\n    function uint2str(uint _i) internal pure returns (string memory _uintAsString) {\n            if (_i == 0) {\n                return \"0\";\n            }\n            uint j = _i;\n            uint len;\n            while (j != 0) {\n                len++;\n                j /= 10;\n            }\n            bytes memory bstr = new bytes(len);\n            uint k = len - 1;\n            while (_i != 0) {\n                bstr[k--] = byte(uint8(48 + _i % 10));\n                _i /= 10;\n            }\n            return string(bstr);\n    }\n\n    function getProposalByIndex(uint proposal) view public returns(string[5] memory) {\n        Proposal memory p = proposals[proposal];\n\n        string memory progress = uint2str(p.progress);\n        string memory votesUpWeight = uint2str(p.votesUpWeight);\n        string memory votesDownWeight = uint2str(p.votesDownWeight);\n\n        return [p.description, p.url, progress, votesUpWeight, votesDownWeight];\n    }\n\n    function updateProgress(uint proposal, uint progress) public {\n        require(proposals[proposal].progress < progress);\n        require(proposals[proposal].owner == msg.sender);\n        proposals[proposal].progress = progress;\n    }\n}\n\ninterface IStakingAuRa {\n
